item.description:
In part 7 of this series, we saw a warning in the search results:
&ldquo;no matching index found, create an index to optimize query time&rdquo;
This is Cloudant&rsquo;s polite way of saying that your query is expensive and the database is having to walk through the whole data set to calculate the answer. In small databases this is not a problem but in a production system, with the data growing all the time, an index is essential.
